        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>[TOC]</p><h2 id="1-使用Python作科学计算-scientific-python"><a href="#1-使用Python作科学计算-scientific-python" class="headerlink" title="1. 使用Python作科学计算(scientific python)"></a>1. 使用Python作科学计算(scientific python)</h2><ul><li>在scripts前习惯添加如下代码 :</li></ul><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> __future__ <span class="keyword">import</span> division</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> matplotlib.pyplot <span class="keyword">as</span> plt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>使用 pickle module 读取数据：</li></ul><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> pickle</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">data = &#123;<span class="string">'stim'</span>: np.array([<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">3</span>]), <span class="string">'response'</span>: np.array([<span class="number">4</span>,<span class="number">5</span>,<span class="number">6</span>])&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> open(<span class="string">'my_data.pickle'</span>,<span class="string">'wb'</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">    pickle.dump(data,f)</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> open(<span class="string">'my_data.pickle'</span>,<span class="string">'rb'</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">new_data = pickle.load(f)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="2-Models-used-in-CN"><a href="#2-Models-used-in-CN" class="headerlink" title="2. Models used in CN"></a>2. Models used in CN</h2><h3 id="Models"><a href="#Models" class="headerlink" title="Models"></a>Models</h3><ul><li>Desciptive Models—— what nervous system do</li><li>Mechnistic Models——how they function</li><li>Interpretive Models——why they operate in particular ways</li></ul><h3 id="Receptive-Fields-Experiment"><a href="#Receptive-Fields-Experiment" class="headerlink" title="Receptive Fields.Experiment"></a>Receptive Fields.Experiment</h3><p>Example to explain: ——Receptive Fields</p><p>​    Hubel and Wiesel, c. 1965    </p><p>​    <img src="C:\Users\chuhu\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\1557565822760.png" alt="1557565822760"></p><p>​        showed that the cat’s cell responded rebustly when the bar of light oriented at 45° </p><p><img src="C:\Users\chuhu\AppData\Roaming\Typora\typora-user-images\1557566193300.png" alt="1557566193300"></p><p>​    感受野，感受器受刺激兴奋时，通过感受器官中的向心神经元将神经冲动（各种感觉信息）传到上位中枢，一个神经元所反应（支配）的刺激区域就叫做神经元的感受野（receptive field）【受纳野】。</p><h3 id="Receptive-Fields-Models"><a href="#Receptive-Fields-Models" class="headerlink" title="Receptive Fields.Models"></a>Receptive Fields.Models</h3><ul><li><p>Desp</p><ul><li><p>Retina 视网膜</p><p>layer of tissue back of your eyes</p><ul><li></li></ul></li></ul></li><li><p>Mach</p></li><li><p>Interp</p></li></ul>]]></content>
      
      
